fields.title: It is over cast, and dreary...
Trees whip back and forth in the wind. It's odd, because fog settles over the land calmly. The river nearby seems to grow...
Imagine you went to the zoo and could take home any animal for the day.  Tell a story about your time together, and the wisdom the animal holds.
Have you ever been proud of something that you knew you would get in trouble for? Write about it...
A blessing in disguise (but for the wrong person), ends up benefiting the enemy.
